=Definition=


Thomas Wayburn:

"The abandonment by all of society of individual competition for personal wealth and power is a necessary and sufficient condition for sustainable happiness for all of humanity.  Any method whatever for achieving this is dematerialism."
(http://dematerialism.net/)



=Key Book To Read=

''On the Preservation of Species'' [http://dematerialism.net/POS.html] By Thomas Wayburn.


